  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of T-817MA in Patients With Mild to Moderate Alzheimer's Disease (US202)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2 Multi-center, Randomized, Double Blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel Group Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of T-817MA in Patients With Mild to Moderate Alzheimer's Disease</official_title>
